Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我缺少两年间的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且也无法行走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我听说原因是遇到了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当我渐渐熟悉了轮椅上的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}父母又由于工作原因决定搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以这副身躯搬到无人认识的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拯救了几乎要被不安击垮的我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正是友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道要住在这里的人就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我们就是新邻居啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫结城友奈 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫东乡美森
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡…真是帅气的姓氏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我与友奈一同就读赞州中学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天都很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风学姐邀请我们加入勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了大家鼓起勇气做好事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在勇者社中与大家一同度过的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我的珍宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过这种日常在某一天突然结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们成了真正的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不知道 这已经是第二次了Comment: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,OP-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:57.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}サカラバ　サア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:02.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}静けき森の中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:08.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}いま目覚めた花たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:14.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}この世に何を思い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:21.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}何を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:25.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}ああ　真実ほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:33.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}人を魅了するものはないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:37.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}ああ　真実ほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:44.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}人に残酷なものもないのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}咲き誇れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:50.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}想いのままに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:53.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:57.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}全てを赌けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:03:02.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}無限の星すらも霞むように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:08.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}勇気　心に溢れ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:18.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}いかなる時も生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:57.05,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}盛开吧 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:02.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}静谧的森林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:08.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}刚醒来的花儿们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:14.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}如何看待这世间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:21.12,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}有什么样的感触
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:25.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}没有什么比真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:33.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}更加让人心醉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:37.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}没有什么比真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:44.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}更加对人残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}尽情绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:50.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}随心飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:53.57,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}在此瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:57.10,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}拼上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:03:02.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}遮蔽无限星空的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:08.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}勇气充满心间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:18.04,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}永远生活下去
