Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是吧 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 姐姐你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…大家的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被选中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种现象被称为树海化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}时间停滞下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被选为勇者的我们被送往神树大人所创造的结界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦派遣来的风学姐将勇者适应值较高的少女收集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}创立了勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者为了让世界免受Vertex这一神秘生命体的袭击而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一旦Vertex抵达神树大人 世界就会毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了阻止它 我们展现出战斗的意志 成为神树大人的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界说不定会毁灭 大家也面临着危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而我却没能展现出意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而 友奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看着别人受到伤害 经历苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与其让别人经历这样的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不如由我来努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者冲拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社的活动内容是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了大家鼓起勇气做好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是赞州中学勇者社 结城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我来成为勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没跟你们说真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那怎么不早点把勇者社真正的意义告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈和树说不定会死的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是就算勇者适应性再高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪个小队会被神树大人选中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在敌人来之前是无法知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为这是涉及人类存亡的头等大事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直瞒着我们…这么重要的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是只有我一个人无法变身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就会成为勇者社的累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对输给恐惧的自己感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对风学姐说了过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为正是由于适应性让我与风学姐和树相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是因为这适应性？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以后也会很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是多了有点困难的任务而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很高兴与大家相识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保护这个世界是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倘若我也有保护我珍爱的朋友的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要欺负友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}据风学姐所说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要打倒十二只Vertex 我们的任务也就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且大赦还派遣了经过特别训练的夏凛加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一开始对勇者社持否定态度的夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也渐渐地敞开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家度过着珍爱的日常 憧憬着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要保护好这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剩下七只
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么全部都攻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是最糟糕的袭击模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出阵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 去歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们也上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}将积蓄的能量释放出来 就是勇者的王牌「盛开」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}通过不断地盛开 勇者的力量将得到增幅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦是这样说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}面对着剩下的七只Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们相继地盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「盛开」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了庆祝勇者社大胜利 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目标达成之后的果汁果然就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那场战斗中经历了盛开的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体都出现了异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈是味觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风学姐是左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树是声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是左耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然大赦的医生说应该马上就会痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但却完全没有好转的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后 我知道了勇者系统的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直在呼唤你呀 鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是想死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她的名字叫做乃木园子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她用那悲伤的眼神紧盯着我 称呼我为鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈经历过「盛开」对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一下开放 一下变强的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对 经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们觉得绽放盛开的花之后会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛开之后 身体应该有什么部位会变得不方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我觉得大赦的人们掩盖这一系统也算是一种同情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过 我真的好想被好好告知这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是早知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就会更珍惜和朋友玩耍的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个发带真适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这条发带是非常重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只记得这些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突然叫我们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有东西想给风学姐和友奈看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东…东乡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者绝不会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了确认前代勇者乃木园子所言是否属实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我使用了各种手段寻死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz28.62\move(478,250,458,-24,0,3253)}切腹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz28.62\move(528,322,508,60,41,3253)}上吊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz26.03\move(646,376,626,110,41,3253)}跳楼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frz21.5\frx320\fry354\move(788,420,776,154,41,3253)}一氧化碳中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx320\fry354\frz29.6\move(670,552,650,288,41,3253)}淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx320\fry354\frz29.6\move(706,634,686,366,41,3253)}服毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无论尝试何种方法 精灵都成功地阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}精灵并不是为了保护勇者 而是为了将勇者永远束缚在其使命上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说 乃木园子所言属实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的后遗症是盛开这一力量的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是供品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 树就再也无法发出声音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了保护别人而献上自己的身躯进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都怪我把树拉进勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.24,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}出会えてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:13.26,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}木漏れ日 眩しい森の中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:18.38,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}風はいつもあったかくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:25.03,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}心ほぐれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:31.13,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}こんな日々がずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:37.82,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:46.11,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}広がる空は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:51.00,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}愛や希望で溢れて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:57.51,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この声が届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:03.90,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌い続けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:14.18,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いつも　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:28.11,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この声が届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:33.91,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌い続けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:44.61,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いつも　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.24,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}庆幸与你邂逅于
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:13.26,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}光斑炫目的林间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:18.38,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}风总是那么温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:25.03,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}心灵也随之解放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:31.13,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}但愿这样的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:37.82,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}永远地持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:46.11,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如此广阔的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:51.00,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}充满着爱与希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:57.51,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我会不停地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:03.90,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直至传入你心间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:14.18,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一直一直感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:28.11,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我会不停地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:33.91,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直至传入你心间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:44.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一直一直感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听我说…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是说有未来的梦想了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那快告诉姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不会跟别人说的 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一天会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要干掉大赦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦欺骗了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛开的后遗症是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么非得受这份罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么非得让树失声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么非得放弃梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拯救了世界的代价就是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想看到风学姐伤害别人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种事情怎能饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是即便是告知我们会有后遗症
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们还是会战斗下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了保卫世界只能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有人有别的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:46.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs30\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(504,252,240,74,0,4289)}要是没有与勇者社的大家相遇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:46.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs30\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(462,370,216,196,35,4289)}一定也不会拥有想歌唱的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:46.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs30\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(558,560,312,398,35,4289)}能加入勇者社真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你冷静地听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我来告诉你墙壁外侧的秘密 这个世界的构成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我觉得真相还是由你自己的眼睛来见证比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她所说的都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界在宇宙规模的结界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Vertex无限再生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们一边奉献着身体的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一边重复着永无止尽的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而最终…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体就像树木一样无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最终就像这样被侍奉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我得出的结论是破坏墙壁打倒神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要从勇者这一祭品中摆脱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就只有破坏神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我无法忍受大家再受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么…还要坚持…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道为什么 突然想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不论是家里的事还是勇者社的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把麻烦事都交给姐姐来做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 其实我想让自己能与姐姐并肩前行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何止是并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知不觉间已经走到我前面了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么无法变身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不配当…朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不再作为大赦的勇者而战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从现在开始作为勇者社的一员而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不会让我们的勇者社遭到毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想看到友奈哭泣的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}诸行无常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来吧 好戏从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}远处的家伙们听好了 近处的家伙们看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是赞州中学二年级生 勇者社社员三好夏凛的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来 吃招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这即将来临的新世界中 风学姐和树就不需要再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社五准则 其五
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有志者事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛也不要再失去什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:19:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个世界 大赦的做法 有多么凄惨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要拯救我们 就只有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「谢谢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我长期以来一直接受勇者的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有战斗才是我的存在价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是多亏了大家 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈你能够改变东乡的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定能够
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我曾经作为勇者战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后失去了这段记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然我保护不了我最好的朋友 那我就做不成勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要能将一切终结 我们的人间地狱也会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与其牺牲友奈和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}与其再次忘记这珍爱的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我永远陪伴着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样的话就不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做了这么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是东乡同学的错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们去阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}绝对不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 在这关键的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风学姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欢迎回来 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.43,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要小看勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 勇者社…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\alpha&HA0&}友奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}击中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社的大家 明明也都很艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但却为了朋友 拼尽全力 阻止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈全力冲向了我 全力抱紧了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后我们击败了敌人 身体功能也恢复了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我重要的回忆 也恢复了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.47,0:23:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然还不清楚为什么会恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但至少这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为失去的生命 并没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起去上学 学习 玩耍 回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}日常竟然是如此珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很清楚 一切并没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Vertex还残存着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道未来还会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是现在 我紧紧地拥抱着这无可替代的温暖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.89,0:22:45.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}さあ　歩き出そう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.20,0:22:48.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}みんなで見た　あの空模様
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.30,0:22:51.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}光のカーテン　しめきっても
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.91,0:22:53.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここは暗くない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.80,0:22:55.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もう　分かってたの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.80,0:22:58.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつか終わる　この瞬間
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.89,0:23:02.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}とても大切で　大切で
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.70,0:23:04.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}目を背けていた
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.11,0:23:07.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}儚い時は
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.20,0:23:10.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっという間に過ぎて行くよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.09,0:23:12.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}これは本当に
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.13,0:23:15.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}起こった出来事？
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そのカケラを夕陽に
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.88,0:23:20.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}かざして確かめてみるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れられない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れちゃいけない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.64,0:23:32.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとつひとつが素晴らしい思い出
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.67,0:23:37.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつでも　目に浮かぶその笑顔
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.20,0:23:43.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとつひとつが奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.60,0:23:49.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここにこうして舞い降りてきたの
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.94,0:23:55.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So bright
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.89,0:22:45.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}来　迈开脚步吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.20,0:22:48.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}大家看到的天空
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.30,0:22:51.91,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}即便拉上光之帘
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.91,0:22:53.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这里也并不黑暗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.80,0:22:55.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我现在已经明白
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.80,0:22:58.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这瞬间终将结束
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.89,0:23:02.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这是那么的宝贵
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.70,0:23:04.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我不禁避开视线
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.11,0:23:07.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}梦幻般的时刻
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.20,0:23:10.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}真是转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.09,0:23:12.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这是真真正正
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.13,0:23:15.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}发生过的事吗
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}残片对着夕阳
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.88,0:23:20.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}来试着确认吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这些无法忘却
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这些不能忘却
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.64,0:23:32.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}每每都是美妙回忆
